1.title: Industrial Storage Tank

episode of.title: You Can't Turn That Into a House (TV Series 2017– )

1.plot: Brothers Rehan and Taimoor renovate up a storm in Tornado Alley attempting to convert a rusty metal storage tank into a luxury country getaway. Will miscalculated measurements, abrupt additions and mounds of mud totally tank their plans?

2.title: Bison Shed

episode of.title: You Can't Turn That Into a House (TV Series 2017– )

2.plot: Brothers Taimoor and Rehan find themselves in a hairy situation as they attempt to merge an old bison shed and a disused shipping container into one trendy two-story hangout for two teenage daughters.

3.title: School Buses

episode of.title: You Can't Turn That Into a House (TV Series 2017– )

3.plot: Brothers Rehan and Taimoor saddle up on a bucking bull ranch in Cypress, Texas to try and transform two busted school buses into a dream home for Will and Tana.

4.title: Dairy Trucks

episode of.title: You Can't Turn That Into a House (TV Series 2017– )

4.plot: Brothers Taimoor and Rehan find themselves in a sour spot as they attempt to convert two decrepit dairy trucks into one sweet retreat. Will these milkmen fail to deliver?

5.title: Carnival Trailer

episode of.title: You Can't Turn That Into a House (TV Series 2017– )

5.plot: Brothers Taimoor and Rehan have to reign in their frustrations as they attempt to transform a mini-horse trailer into a glorious guesthouse for Grandma.

6.title: Dumpster

episode of.title: You Can't Turn That Into a House (TV Series 2017– )

6.plot: Brothers Taimoor and Rehan are taking on their smelliest job ever as they attempt to transform a rusty old dumpster into a chic musicians' sanctuary. Will the homeowners decide it's a stinky disaster or will our guys be able to salvage their grand design and to prove everyone wrong who says, "You Can't Turn That Dumpster Into A House?"

episode of.title: You Can't Turn That Into a House (TV Series 2017– )

7.plot: Brothers Taimoor and Rehan take on the riskiest build of their careers as they attempt to convert two massive grain bins for contractor Kyle's picky in-laws.

episode of.title: You Can't Turn That Into a House (TV Series 2017– )

8.plot: Brothers Taimoor and Rehan have set their sights on converting a disused giant grain bin into a rustic hunting retreat. Will these marksmen miss their bullseye and wind up with a rusted out disaster?

11.plot: Brothers Taimoor and Rehan flock to Lee's Summit Missouri to try and convert a grungy chicken coop into a minimalist mansion. Will their plans crack trying to give an artistic student an awe-inspiring dorm-alternative?
